%EDITMAC  ------------------ T         MACRO  ------------------------  TUTORIAL
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD                                                             +
+
+THE%T+MACRO IS USED TO PLACE THE TIME AND DATE IN THE SHORT MESSAGE AREA OF
+THE CURRENT EDIT PANEL.
+
+USE:
+TYPE%T+ON THE COMMAND LINE
+
%EDIT ---- THIS.DATA.SET                                 COLUMNS 001 072
%COMMAND ===> T                                         SCROLL ===> CSR
+***************************** TOP OF DATA *************************************
+
%RESULT:
%EDIT ---- THIS.DATA.SET                               22:32:55 08/28/88
%COMMAND ===> T                                         SCROLL ===> CSR
+***************************** TOP OF DATA *************************************
+
)PROC
&KEY = .PFKEY
)END
